How do I update this listing?




                                             Hendershot Investments is based out of Bristow. Hendershot Investments is a large advisory firm with  More than 100 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $294,590,114 (Form ADV from 2017-03-24).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q2 2017 included $222,671,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 42.51%. Hendershot Investments's largest holding is Berkshire Hathaway Inc Class B with shares held of 91,014.  Hendershot Investments has met the qualifications for inclusion in our WhaleScore system.    WhaleWisdom has at least 27 13F filings in our database for Hendershot Investments. 
                                           






